<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AnoTS OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
        }

        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #4285F4;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .custom-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #4285F4;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #3367d6;
        }

        .separator {
            display: block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #ccc;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="welcome-message">OTP FROM ANOTS</div>
        <div class="custom-message">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{username}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your OTP: <strong>{{OTP}}</strong></p>
            <p><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> Please keep your OTP confidential. Do not share it with anyone.</p>
            <p>OTP valid in 20 minutes!</p>
            <p>from AnoTS to {{email}}</p>
        </div>
        <span class="separator"></span>
        <p class="signature">Best regards,<br>The AnoTS team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
